{"tid":1060641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美加停飛波音737 MAX系列客機","createTime":"2019-03-14T00:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T12:32:53.000Z","uid":15564,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8af04faed7a867537a50ec91b52a8de8538c2dae","tid":1060641,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T00:47:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國及加拿大宣布停飛涉及埃塞俄比亞空難的波音737 MAX 8客機。美國總統特朗普強調，美方重視航空安全。<br />\n<br />\n美國及加拿大在全球約40個國家及地區停飛737 MAX系列客機後，才跟隨發出禁飛令。美國同時禁飛737 MAX 9客機。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦航空管理局早一日仍然指客機安全，<span style=\"color: red;\">但周三發緊急命令，指分析過新衛星圖片及證據後，認為遇難的埃塞俄比亞航空客機飛行表現及路線都跟去年10月墜落爪哇海的印尼獅子航空客機非常相似</span>，重申之前收到的數據未足以支持作出禁飛決定。<br />\n<br />\n美國被質疑，為顧及波音企業利益而遲遲未禁飛737 MAX，<span style=\"color: red;\">特朗普亦無作過相關表態，僅表示客機設計應該簡單些。</span><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=340765&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D340765%26refer%3DShare&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=3ffbadae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D340765%26refer%3DShare&h=4fe901ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=340765&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n侵侵教波音整飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba755ef32c110e43bc1f7ad2f7f7d5cd90676b91","tid":1060641,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T00:55:33.000Z","msg":"其實好多時的空難，就正正係因為機械的人工智能系統出錯，或感應器問題"},{"pid":"b031d6f0cd9ec083d2e3c13f8bb0fc996d8b0ac2","tid":1060641,"uid":56561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T01:08:14.000Z","msg":"加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd719f8d72a7e1ff3f18b9157ebae9ec89729b6","tid":1060641,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ba755ef32c110